	<h1 class="title">小鱼形状的外带酱油包是如何火起来的？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-02-09 08:03:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/6009/medium/6009.jpg?1436692209" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="6009" data-title="《小鱼形状的外带酱油包是如何火起来的？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6009/medium/6009.jpg?1436692209" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6009.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
